---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Support — Gardn"
  description="Help when you need it. Email help@gardn.world for app questions, hello@gardn.world for partnerships and press."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 pt-20 pb-32 md:pt-28 md:pb-40">
    <p class="text-eyebrow text-gardn-fern">Help, when you need it.</p>
    <h1 class="text-h1 text-gardn-forest-deep mt-4" style="text-wrap: balance;">
      We're here.
    </h1>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-6">
      <p class="text-body text-gardn-muted">
        Most questions about Gardn are answered fastest by email. We read every message, and we usually reply the same day.
      </p>

      <p class="text-body text-gardn-forest-deep">
        <strong class="font-semibold">Email</strong> —
        <a
          href="mailto:help@gardn.world"
          class="underline decoration-gardn-fern decoration-2 underline-offset-4 hover:text-gardn-forest"
        >help@gardn.world</a>
      </p>

      <p class="text-body text-gardn-muted">
        If something's gone wrong inside the app — a crash, a bug, advice that didn't fit your garden — send a screenshot if you can. It helps us see what you're seeing.
      </p>

      <p class="text-body text-gardn-muted">
        For app reviews, partnership enquiries, and press, we're at
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@gardn.world"
          class="underline decoration-gardn-fern decoration-2 underline-offset-4 hover:text-gardn-forest"
        >hello@gardn.world</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
